Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可愛了～～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是小金悄悄的好好的拍下來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張是直接用手抓東西吃的雛莓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張是翠星石換衣服的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓她發現而稍微費了點事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇少女的人偶們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～要是大家能馬上來我家裡就好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:01:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也該認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之  現在還是應該慎重的步步為營吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣  像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要每個地方都揉到是訣竅的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揉了一圈又一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做出好吃的餅乾來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  小雛做得真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  要不要一起來做餅乾？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅不可能來做的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會拿「不要  會把裙子弄髒的」\N之類的理由拒絕的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  就像我說的一樣的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一大跳的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅竟然自己說要來做餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是吹的什麼風的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只…只是心血來潮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有什麼別的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不過  真紅穿圍裙好適合哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我要做些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就來揉麵團吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——我看不下去了的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這成什麼樣子的說嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個餅乾的麵團而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想要違抗我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…好大的煙哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼的說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第…第一次做總會不順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好了！快把窗戶打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過456次失敗後總算等到這一天了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們見識見識小金真正的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——真  真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是金絲雀哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來做什麼的說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小金是來…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正…正好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都在這裡  就趁著這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我認真地來做你們的對手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  烤好了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餅乾做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得有這個機會  一起嘗嘗如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來我最完美的傑作已經烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀  把我的餅乾端上來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是翠星石做的看起來最好吃的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛的花蛋餅乾也烤得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…什麼？豬嗎？…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失禮！這是庫庫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫庫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒想到事情會進展成這種形式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超出我的考慮範圍了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…你到底在想什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  小金絲雀  趁熱吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是小雛做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該…該不會  在這個餅乾裡做了什麼手腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧…嘻嘻嘻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我…我可不會上你們的當！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道說  真正的圈套在這紅茶裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不知怎麼突然很想睡覺了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著現在  拿走這個傢伙的薔薇聖母的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還自稱什麼謀士  真可笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  笨蛋笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小伎倆對我薔薇少女中第一的頭腦派金絲雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來呀來呀  這些也吃掉的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難吃——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個餅乾是真紅做的的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「果然」是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也拚命去做了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下次一定會更好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真紅…有點…奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也不錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這就要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就這樣放過你們吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定會把你們都擊敗的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下次就烤些司康餅等著你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(scone：一種英式風味的小型圓餅  製作較為簡單)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！真紅完全把我當傻瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金絲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這次要邀請我去野餐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和真紅不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告訴我一件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想要和我們戰鬥麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此你又想怎麼樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你是這個意思的話就沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  有一件事請你記住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行愛麗絲遊戲之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會有人離開我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會再回到現在這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事你不說我也知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——？真紅她們烤餅乾？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  這都能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要吃真紅做的比較好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大家來我家裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要和她們一起做飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓她們穿各種各樣的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍很多很多照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——光是想著就——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到她們的話  就一定要勝出愛麗絲遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果這麼做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行愛麗絲遊戲之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會有人離開我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會再回到現在這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…如果  小金不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小金不能動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  變成那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有小金的日子我過不下去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會死掉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷  冷靜點  小美！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不願意！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金要一直陪在我身邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣  就不能對她們聽之任之了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戰鬥的話  就沒法得到她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀——摩擦生熱讓臉燒起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊……今天要住下來的說嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:10:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺他們在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石  你在做什麼的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:34.72,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夢の中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:42.61,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}生まれた心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}誕生於夢中的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:47.20,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}カラス窗が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:51.25,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}君見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}玻璃窗上映出你的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:57.59,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}瞬のウチに迂めて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}在一瞬間充滿心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠  今天心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又沒吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒我再來拿  至少要吃一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為只要唱歌我就會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…原來如此  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？…啊  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來得正好  現在可以看到好東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧  讓他們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正要賦予那個人偶「生命」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「生命」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面為大家播放各地送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀罕的影像和各種活動的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大花園～喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻嘻…活該的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說謊  我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天你明顯的改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而應該說是「察覺到了」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「察覺到了」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該做什麼  我想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…想做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金絲雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始愛麗絲遊戲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一樂章  攻擊之華爾茲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不點莓！快點給我起來的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是第二樂章！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊的巴洛克！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！耳朵好難受哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！金絲雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不發火你就亂搞一氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撥弦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪斯科！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該結束了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金絲雀  快停下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀！快放開！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饒不了你的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要毀掉你的小提琴的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲劇的變奏曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們承認失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且今後聽從我的命令的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我停手也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我們會乖乖的服從你的說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  所以我才要打倒你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了小美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定要取得勝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終樂章  破壞之交響曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快停手的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金…金絲…雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是認真的  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠這些花瓣是沒辦法擋住我的聲音的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個被你搞得一團亂的房間  快點收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我我知道了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…櫻田小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總  總算是做完了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！這叫自作自受的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對翠星石等人無禮的懲罰的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你想把我們打倒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美想要得到你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小美小姐得到我們之後想要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩  一起做飯  換衣服什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這個問題就能夠解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  這件事剛才已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  資料已經通過郵件確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我再好好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？喂喂？喂喂？怎麼了？然後呢？然後…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…？喂喂——？喂喂——？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金把她們帶回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是跟你一起來了而已的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是小美小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是做夢而是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是真正的好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊  這個這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是為了讓大家來的時候穿而買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來穿上吧來穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  讓我拍照！拜託了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來別碰我別靠近我的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  好棒  太棒了  各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說這也太放任她了的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅～翠星石～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最棒了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是金絲雀的媒介呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看得出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛好高興哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…是嗎？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…人類真是什麼樣的都有的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真感動！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都眼花繚亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美是攝影的專家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多其它的衣服想讓你們穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要拍很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  玩的真高興哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  被她好好的擺弄了一通的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:20:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你沒有戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有戰鬥的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  金絲雀是來進行愛麗絲遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是宿命的話還是會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再失去什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我不會再戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要放棄愛麗絲遊戲嗎  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！父親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！那是翠星石平時坐的地方的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我才不管吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我薔薇少女中第一的頭腦派金絲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想坐在這裡就要可以坐在這裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…你這個小不點人偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼任性的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石也說點什麼的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？蒼星石  不在的說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純也不在吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  薔薇少女  夢見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如夢中所見吧？
